.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
7 different pets are kept: goldfish, bird, lizard, horse, guinea-pig, rabbit, goat
 1. the owner of the rabbit is the owner of the rabbit##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
 3. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
 4. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
 5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 6. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
 7. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 9. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| Pet   | horse | bird | rabbit | goat | lizard | goldfish | guinea-pig |

