.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-3::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: december, july, august, october, june, april, may
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in july##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##8
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Birthday   | june | april | october | may | december | august | july |

