.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-4::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: hiking, fishing, filmmaking, drawing, traveling, photography, skydiving
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
10. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |  2  |   3   |    4     |   5   |   6    |  7   |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | hiking | drawing | skydiving | traveling | fishing | photography |

